00:16:03.440 --> 00:16:09.940
Of course, I was on the other end of the line.

315
00:16:09.940 --> 00:16:13.240
Thanks to you, now I know full well,

316
00:16:13.240 --> 00:16:15.140
that you aren't just normal brats

