he is keeping his mother company

322
00:16:27.040 --> 00:16:29.840
as I tied him up in the restroom as well.

323
00:16:29.840 --> 00:16:31.040
Well, at any rate,

324
00:16:31.040 --> 00:16:34.940
you guys will soon join them in that same restroom.

325
00:16:37.040 --> 00:16:39.440
You, girl, with the hair band.

326
00:16:39.440 --> 00:16:43.640
Tie your friends up with that sticky tape.

327
00:16:43.640 --> 00:16:45.540
After all that's done,

328
00:16:45.540 --> 00:16:47.740
I'll tie you up myself.

