354
00:17:58.440 --> 00:18:00.740
Sure, I'm buzzing you up now.

355
00:18:03.140 --> 00:18:05.440
So it wasn't Conan.

356
00:18:06.440 --> 00:18:10.040
I thought he'd come for us after he read the email we sent.

357
00:18:10.040 --> 00:18:12.740
But, I've finally figured it out

358
00:18:12.740 --> 00:18:16.740
that you two are trying to destroy evidence pertaining to tax evasion.

359
00:18:17.940 --> 00:18:20.040
The sender of that registered mail

360
00:18:20.040 --> 00:18:22.040
was the previous resident of this apartment, the one named Uemura,

361
00:18:22.040 --> 00:18:24.440
who was a former employee of the Isobe Corporation,

362
00:18:24.440 --> 00:18:27.640
now under suspicion of tax evasion.

363
00:18:27.640 --> 00:18:29.040
The contents of the registered mail

364
00:18:29.040 --> 00:18:31.040
are probably whistle-blower documents,

365
00:18:31.040 --> 00:18:34.240
or account books with evidence of tax evasion.

366
00:18:34.240 --> 00:18:36.440
It was sent approximately two weeks ago,

367
00:18:36.440 --> 00:18:38.440
in exchange for a reward,

368
00:18:38.440 --> 00:18:41.940
to a producer at Nichiuri TV named Hida.

369
00:18:41.940 --> 00:18:46.640
The employee planned to move from here and go into hiding.

370
00:18:46.640 --> 00:18:50.440
But that producer ended up in a car accident

371
00:18:50.440 --> 00:18:53.240
and couldn't receive the registered mail due to being hospitalized.

372
00:18:53.240 --> 00:18:57.640
Since the post office holds on to mail for more or less ten days.

373
00:18:57.640 --> 00:19:00.340
You calculated the time of its return.

374
00:19:00.340 --> 00:19:03.740
And plotted to pose as Uemura who had lived here before,

375
00:19:03.740 --> 00:19:06.840
and snatch away that registered mail.

376
00:19:06.840 --> 00:19:10.040
Then, what happened to that Mr. Uemura?

377
00:19:10.040 --> 00:19:12.140
Probably confined somewhere else,

378
00:19:12.140 --> 00:19:15.540
or already murdered.

379
00:19:15.540 --> 00:19:17.840
And made to look like an accident,

380
00:19:17.840 --> 00:19:20.840
similar to the Nichiuri TV producer.

381
00:19:20.840 --> 00:19:24.440
My, look at you, so I was right on the mark.

382
00:19:32.140 --> 00:19:33.440
He's at the door.

383
00:19:33.440 --> 00:19:34.440
Take it from him.

384
00:19:34.440 --> 00:19:35.940
Sure.

385
00:19:39.440 --> 00:19:43.040
Anyway, as for what we'll do with you...

386
00:19:43.040 --> 00:19:46.940
I suppose we'll decide after we've checked out the registered mail.

387
00:19:57.540 --> 00:20:00.440
Did something happen?

388
00:20:00.440 --> 00:20:01.440
Hey.

389
00:20:12.140 --> 00:20:13.840
Hey, Conan, don't go in before me...

390
00:20:13.840 --> 00:20:15.740
Cuff that woman, hurry.

391
00:20:15.740 --> 00:20:16.740
Okay.

392
00:20:17.840 --> 00:20:19.840
Conan!

393
00:20:24.940 --> 00:20:26.840
Where's the woman that was here?

394
00:20:30.040 --> 00:20:32.440
I put her to sleep with my tranquilizer gun.

395
00:20:32.440 --> 00:20:34.940
And she's being handcuffed right now,

396
00:20:34.940 --> 00:20:38.040
by Officer Takagi who's dressed in that mailman disguise.

397
00:20:39.340 --> 00:20:41.340
By the way, if you're asking

398
00:20:41.340 --> 00:20:43.740
